    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in poor condition and is recommended only for those looking for a serious project or a source for parts. The engine currently struggles to stay idling and will likely require a full rebuild or replacement to be reliable. Visually, the car has significant rust through the floorboards and wheel wells, and the interior upholstery is heavily torn and stained. It is being sold strictly as-is, with no warranties expressed or implied.",
